  "subject": "1.10.0 container release",
  "commit_message": "1.10.0 container release\n\n- add release notes for the docs\n- OpenTelemetry instrumentation for all CDS services\n- CBA lifecycle management improvements\n- REST client response header capture\n- Workflow execution page and deployed tab in Designer UI\n- 14 CDS Designer UI fixes and improvements\n- Playwright e2e tests for cds-ui\n- Increased py-executor and command-executor test coverage\n- Maven dependency consolidation and cleanup\n- Python dependency management improvements\n- Docs modernisation: Mermaid diagrams, Sphinx config update\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-4199\nChange-Id: I359920faa25d1873d7d241bbc9856316cc443059\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
